National City Corp projected income ofeight mln dlrs for the second quarter ending June 30 due to a55 mln dlr charge for loan loss provisions.    This compares with earnings in the second quarter of lastyear of 36.3 mln dlrs.    National City said it expects per share income in thesecond quarter to be 20 cts.    The company said it expects full year earnings to becomparable with last year's record 135 mln dlrs.    The bank said its 55 mln dlr special loan loss provision isrelated to loan exposure in less developed countries in itsinternational portfolio. Reuter&#3;